metadata.name: Life
metadata.description: In this NFT I would like to explain life. In our life, we can't recognize how we protect our self from bad energy. Bad energy is everywhere in our life. But our relatives or friends ect. fight against with that bad energy. The water drop in the middle of the NFT is represent us and the water drops colours means the personalities of us and the shape of sun represent of the shield that our surroundings.
